prodNameC: "代首林" 黃體化激素放射免疫分析試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Anti-LH antibody-coated tubes: 2 x 50 tubes. 
I-125-labeled monoclonal anti-LH antibody: The vial contains 370 kBq, of I-125-labled immunoglobulins in buffer with bovine serum albumin.
Standards: The standard vials contain from 0 to 180 IU/L of LH in horse serum.  
Control sera: (lyophilized). The vial contains human LH lyophilized in human serum.
Wash solution (20x): Concentrated solution has to be diluted before use.
applicantName: 泰歷藥品儀器股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市大同區承德路二段81號15樓
efficacy: 使用放射免疫分析法，體外檢測人體血清和血漿中黃體化激素的含量。
